I might not be bad.

30:19.485 --> 30:22.556
I never get better because
I'm never given the chance.

30:22.589 --> 30:23.957
But I could be good.

30:23.990 --> 30:26.092
You know, I mean,
I know I could be good.

30:28.128 --> 30:30.864
But it's not my fault
you get picked last.

30:31.632 --> 30:33.033
Yes, it is.

30:34.568 --> 30:36.770
I mean, you've got
all the power.

30:36.803 --> 30:38.939
You could change
everything.

30:39.740 --> 30:41.441
And how would I do that?

30:42.776 --> 30:44.010
Simple.

30:44.978 --> 30:46.847
Let me pick the teams.

30:51.718 --> 30:54.054
Hey, Lindsay...

30:54.087 --> 30:55.822
I can't take it anymore.

30:55.856 --> 30:57.190
You gotta talk to Kim.

30:57.223 --> 30:59.192
Why? Does she
wanna talk to me?

30:59.225 --> 31:00.493
I don't know,

31:00.527 --> 31:01.728
but you gotta
do something.

31:01.762 --> 31:03.864
She's driving me nuts.

31:03.897 --> 31:07.400
She's bitching nonstop
about her mom, you,

31:07.433 --> 31:08.769
your parents.

31:08.802 --> 31:09.903
I'm dying.

31:09.936 --> 31:11.938
Why is she going
so crazy?

31:11.972 --> 31:13.840
